import React from 'react'
import Layout from '../../components/Layout'
import {Container,Row,Col} from 'react-bootstrap'
/**
* @author
* @function Category
**/

const Category = (props) => {
    return (
        <Layout sidebar>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col md={12}> 

                    </Col>
                </Row>

            </Container>
        </Layout>
    )

}

export default Category
